/docs/padroes/po-ui-quirks#quick-reference--13-known-quirks","content":"po-table"},"2541":{"id":"/docs/padroes/po-ui-quirks-79","page_id":"/docs/padroes/po-ui-quirks","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/padroes/po-ui-quirks#quick-reference--13-known-quirks","content":"**Invisible on first load in OnPush component**"},"2542":{"id":"/docs/padroes/po-ui-quirks-80","page_id":"/docs/padroes/po-ui-quirks","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/padroes/po-ui-quirks#quick-reference--13-known-quirks","content":"Always set `[p-height]` — without it, opacity is set via async `setTimeout` and OnPush never re-renders"},"2543":{"id":"/docs/padroes/po-ui-quirks-81","page_id":"/docs/padroes/po-ui-quirks","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/padroes/po-ui-quirks#quick-reference--13-known-quirks","content":"13"},"2544":{"id":"/docs/padroes/po-ui-quirks-82","page_id":"/docs/padroes/po-ui-quirks","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/padroes/po-ui-quirks#quick-reference--13-known-quirks","content":"po-dynamic-form"},"2545":{"id":"/docs/padroes/po-ui-quirks-83","page_id":"/docs/padroes/po-ui-quirks","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/padroes/po-ui-quirks#quick-reference--13-known-quirks","content":"**`(p-value-change)` silently does nothing**"},"2546":{"id":"/docs/padroes/po-ui-quirks-84","page_id":"/docs/padroes/po-ui-quirks","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/padroes/po-ui-quirks#quick-reference--13-known-quirks","content":"Output doesn't exist — use `(p-form)=\"fn($event)\"` + subscribe `form.valueChanges`"},"2547":{"id":"/docs/padroes/po-ui-quirks-85","page_id":"/docs/padroes/po-ui-quirks","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/padroes/po-ui-quirks#1-po-page-content-blank-on-load-opacity-timing--updated","content":"**Symptom:** Page renders the title/header but ALL content below it is invisible on first\nload (filter bar, tables, buttons — everything inside `ng-content`)."},"2548":{"id":"/docs/padroes/po-ui-quirks-86","page_id":"/docs/padroes/po-ui-quirks","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/padroes/po-ui-quirks#1-po-page-content-blank-on-load-opacity-timing--updated","content":"**Root cause (confirmed by PO-UI source):**\n`PoPageContentComponent` sets `contentOpacity = 0` on creation and calls\n`recalculateHeaderSize()` in `ngAfterViewInit`, which uses `setTimeout` to set\n`contentOpacity = 1`. In **OnPush** components without an async data load (e.g., using\nsynchronous demo data), the component is already \"clean\" when that `setTimeout` fires —\nAngular skips the entire subtree during CD and `contentOpacity = 1` is never reflected\nin the DOM. Components that make HTTP requests are \"accidentally\" safe because the HTTP\nresponse triggers a `markForCheck()` after the `setTimeout` has already run."},"2549":{"id":"/docs/padroes/po-ui-quirks-87","page_id":"/docs/padroes/po-ui-quirks","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/padroes/po-ui-quirks#1-po-page-content-blank-on-load-opacity-timing--updated","content":"**Affects:** Every OnPush component that uses `po-page-default`, `po-page-list`,\n`po-page-edit`, or `po-page-detail` AND loads data synchronously (demo constants, signals\ninitialized at declaration, etc.)."},"2550":{"id":"/docs/padroes/po-ui-quirks-88","page_id":"/docs/padroes/po-ui-quirks","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/padroes/po-ui-quirks#1-po-page-content-blank-on-load-opacity-timing--updated","content":"**Fix — mandatory for every OnPush component using `po-page-*`:**"},"2551":{"id":"/docs/padroes/po-ui-quirks-89","page_id":"/docs/padroes/po-ui-quirks","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/padroes/po-ui-quirks#1-po-page-content-blank-on-load-opacity-timing--updated","content":"**Alternative (when HTTP is used):** the HTTP response auto-triggers `markForCheck()` via\nsignal update, so no explicit `ngAfterViewInit` is needed. But adding it anyway is safe\nand makes the component resilient to future refactors."},"2552":{"id":"/docs/padroes/po-ui-quirks-90","page_id":"/docs/padroes/po-ui-quirks","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/padroes/po-ui-quirks#2-po-input-bottom-padding-misaligns-buttons-8px-offset","content":"**Symptom:** Buttons placed in the same flex row as `po-input` fields appear 8px lower\nthan the visible input field edge, even with `align-items: flex-end` on the container."},"2553":{"id":"/docs/padroes/po-ui-quirks-91","page_id":"/docs/padroes/po-ui-quirks","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/padroes/po-ui-quirks#2-po-input-bottom-padding-misaligns-buttons-8px-offset","content":"**Root cause:** `po-input` renders a wrapper that includes an invisible 8px space below\nthe visible input field, reserved for validation error messages. `flex-end` aligns to the\nbottom of this wrapper (including the invisible 8px), not to the bottom of the visible field."},"2554":{"id":"/docs/padroes/po-ui-quirks-92","page_id":"/docs/padroes/po-ui-quirks","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/padroes/po-ui-quirks#2-po-input-bottom-padding-misaligns-buttons-8px-offset","content":"**Fix:** Add `margin-bottom: 8px` to the button element or its container to push it up\nby the same 8px, aligning it with the visible input bottom edge."},"2555":{"id":"/docs/padroes/po-ui-quirks-93","page_id":"/docs/padroes/po-ui-quirks","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/padroes/po-ui-quirks#2-po-input-bottom-padding-misaligns-buttons-8px-offset","content":"**Measurement verification (Playwright):**"},"2556":{"id":"/docs/padroes/po-ui-quirks-94","page_id":"/docs/padroes/po-ui-quirks","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/padroes/po-ui-quirks#3-po-table-horizontal-scroll-in-side-by-side-panels","content":"**Symptom:** When two `po-table` components are placed side by side (flex:1 each),\neach table generates a horizontal scrollbar even though the specified `p-width` values\nseem reasonable."},"2557":{"id":"/docs/padroes/po-ui-quirks-95","page_id":"/docs/padroes/po-ui-quirks","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/padroes/po-ui-quirks#3-po-table-horizontal-scroll-in-side-by-side-panels","content":"**Root cause:** po-table adds an internal selectable-column (`po-table-column-selectable`)\nof **56px** that is NOT represented in `PoTableColumn[]`. This hidden 56px is added on\ntop of the sum of all `p-width` values, pushing the table wider than its container."},"2558":{"id":"/docs/padroes/po-ui-quirks-96","page_id":"/docs/padroes/po-ui-quirks","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/padroes/po-ui-quirks#3-po-table-horizontal-scroll-in-side-by-side-panels","content":"**Fix (two steps):**"},"2559":{"id":"/docs/padroes/po-ui-quirks-97","page_id":"/docs/padroes/po-ui-quirks","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/padroes/po-ui-quirks#3-po-table-horizontal-scroll-in-side-by-side-panels","content":"**Step 1 — Reduce the internal checkbox column via `::ng-deep`:**"},"2560":{"id":"/docs/padroes/po-ui-quirks-98","page_id":"/docs/padroes/po-ui-quirks","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/padroes/po-ui-quirks#3-po-table-horizontal-scroll-in-side-by-side-panels","content":"**Step 2 — Calculate `p-width` values so that their sum + checkbox = panel width:**"},"2561":{"id":"/docs/padroes/po-ui-quirks-99","page_id":"/docs/padroes/po-ui-quirks","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/padroes/po-ui-quirks#3-po-table-horizontal-scroll-in-side-by-side-panels","content":"**Step 3 — Use gap: 4px (not 8px) between panels** to maximize panel width:"},"2562":{"id":"/docs/padroes/po-ui-quirks-100","page_id":"/docs/padroes/po-ui-quirks","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/padroes/po-ui-quirks#3-po-table-horizontal-scroll-in-side-by-side-panels","content":"**Column width reference at 11px font (8px cell padding per side):**"},"2563":{"id":"/docs/padroes/po-ui-quirks-101","page_id":"/docs/padroes/po-ui-quirks","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/padroes/po-ui-quirks#3-po-table-horizontal-scroll-in-side-by-side-panels","content":"Content"},"2564":{"id":"/docs/padroes/po-ui-quirks-102","page_id":"/docs/padroes/po-ui-quirks","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/padroes/po-ui-quirks#3-po-table-horizontal-scroll-in-side-by-side-panels","content":"Example"},"2565":{"id":"/docs/padroes/po-ui-quirks-103","page_id":"/docs/padroes/po-ui-quirks","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/padroes/po-ui-quirks#3-po-table-horizontal-scroll-in-side-by-side-panels","content":"Minimum width"},"2566":{"id":"/docs/padroes/po-ui-quirks-104","page_id":"/docs/padroes/po-ui-quirks","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/padroes/po-ui-quirks#3-po-table-horizontal-scroll-in-side-by-side-panels","content":"Date"},"2567":{"id":"/docs/padroes/po-ui-quirks-105","page_id":"/docs/padroes/po-ui-quirks","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/padroes/po-ui-quirks#3-po-table-horizontal-scroll-in-side-by-side-panels","content":"\"10/01/2025\""},"2568":{"id":"/docs/padroes/po-ui-quirks-106","page_id":"/docs/padroes/po-ui-quirks","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/padroes/po-ui-quirks#3-po-table-horizontal-scroll-in-side-by-side-panels","content":"84px"},"2569":{"id":"/docs/padroes/po-ui-quirks-107","page_id":"/docs/padroes/po-ui-quirks","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/padroes/po-ui-quirks#3-po-table-horizontal-scroll-in-side-by-side-panels","content":"Currency"},"2570":{"id":"/docs/padroes/po-ui-quirks-108","page_id":"/docs/padroes/po-ui-quirks","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/padroes/po-ui-quirks#3-po-table-horizontal-scroll-in-side-by-side-panels","content":"\"3.200,00\""},"2571":{"id":"/docs/padroes/po-ui-quirks-109","page_id":"/docs/padroes/po-ui-quirks","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/padroes/po-ui-quirks#3-po-table-horizontal-scroll-in-side-by-side-panels","content":"68px"},"2572":{"id":"/docs/padroes/po-ui-quirks-110","page_id":"/docs/padroes/po-ui-quirks","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/padroes/po-ui-quirks#3-po-table-horizontal-scroll-in-side-by-side-panels","content":"Short code 5 chars"},"2573":{"id":"/docs/padroes/po-ui-quirks-111","page_id":"/docs/padroes/po-ui-quirks","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/padroes/po-ui-quirks#3-po-table-horizontal-scroll-in-side-by-side-panels","content":"\"NF00